    "markdown": "---\ntitle: Quarto Movies App\nformat:\n  html:\n    page-layout: full\n    theme:\n      - united\n      - www/styles.scss\n    \nserver: shiny\n---\n\n::: {.cell context='setup'}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell .panel-input}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"form-group shiny-input-container\">\n<label class=\"control-label\" id=\"vars-y-label\" for=\"vars-y\">Y-axis:</label>\n<div>\n<select id=\"vars-y\" class=\"shiny-input-select\"><option value=\"imdb_rating\">IMDB rating</option>\n<option value=\"imdb_num_votes\">IMDB number of votes</option>\n<option value=\"critics_score\">Critics Score</option>\n<option value=\"audience_score\" selected>Audience Score</option>\n<option value=\"runtime\">Runtime</option></select>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"vars-y\" data-nonempty=\"\">{\"plugins\":[\"selectize-plugin-a11y\"]}</script>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"form-group shiny-input-container\">\n<label class=\"control-label\" id=\"vars-x-label\" for=\"vars-x\">X-axis:</label>\n<div>\n<select id=\"vars-x\" class=\"shiny-input-select\"><option value=\"imdb_rating\" selected>IMDB rating</option>\n<option value=\"imdb_num_votes\">IMDB number of votes</option>\n<option value=\"critics_score\">Critics Score</option>\n<option value=\"audience_score\">Audience Score</option>\n<option value=\"runtime\">Runtime</option></select>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"vars-x\" data-nonempty=\"\">{\"plugins\":[\"selectize-plugin-a11y\"]}</script>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"form-group shiny-input-container\">\n<label class=\"control-label\" id=\"vars-z-label\" for=\"vars-z\">Color by:</label>\n<div>\n<select id=\"vars-z\" class=\"shiny-input-select\"><option value=\"title_type\">Title Type</option>\n<option value=\"genre\">Genre</option>\n<option value=\"mpaa_rating\" selected>MPAA Rating</option>\n<option value=\"critics_rating\">Critics Rating</option>\n<option value=\"audience_rating\">Audience Rating</option></select>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"vars-z\" data-nonempty=\"\">{\"plugins\":[\"selectize-plugin-a11y\"]}</script>\n</div>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"shiny-text-output noplaceholder\" id=\"vars-vars\"></pre>\n<div class=\"form-group shiny-input-container\">\n<label class=\"control-label\" id=\"vars-alpha-label\" for=\"vars-alpha\">Alpha:</label>\n<input class=\"js-range-slider\" id=\"vars-alpha\" data-skin=\"shiny\" data-min=\"0\" data-max=\"1\" data-from=\"0.5\" data-step=\"0.1\" data-grid=\"true\" data-grid-num=\"10\" data-grid-snap=\"false\" data-prettify-separator=\",\" data-prettify-enabled=\"true\" data-keyboard=\"true\" data-data-type=\"number\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"form-group shiny-input-container\">\n<label class=\"control-label\" id=\"vars-size-label\" for=\"vars-size\">Size:</label>\n<input class=\"js-range-slider\" id=\"vars-size\" data-skin=\"shiny\" data-min=\"0\" data-max=\"5\" data-from=\"2\" data-step=\"1\" data-grid=\"true\" data-grid-num=\"5\" data-grid-snap=\"false\" data-prettify-separator=\",\" data-prettify-enabled=\"true\" data-keyboard=\"true\" data-data-type=\"number\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"form-group shiny-input-container\">\n<label class=\"control-label\" id=\"vars-plot_title-label\" for=\"vars-plot_title\">Plot title</label>\n<input id=\"vars-plot_title\" type=\"text\" class=\"shiny-input-text form-control\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"Enter plot title\"/>\n</div>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.cell .panel-center}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<br/>\n<div class=\"shiny-plot-output html-fill-item\" id=\"plot-scatterplot\" style=\"width:100%;height:400px;\"></div>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.cell .panel-fill}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<br/>\n```\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<em>\nBuilt using \n<a href=\"https://quarto.org/docs/interactive/shiny/\">\n<img src=\"www/quarto.png\" height=\"25\" width=\"90\" style=\"margin:10px 10px\"/>\n</a>\nand data from the \n<a href=\"https://rstudio-education